> properties.yml
```java
test.map = {key1:'value1',key2:'value2',key3:'value3'}
test.list = value1,value2,value3
```

> 在目标Bean中使用@Value注解进行注入：
```java
@Value("#{'${test.list}'.split(',')}")
private List<String> testList;
@Value("#{${test.map}}")
private Map<String,String> testMap;
``` 




