## 使用

#### 场景一

* 三个操作用异步线程执行，然后`CompletableFuture.allOf()`得到汇总结果，不阻塞主线程

```java
public static void main(String[] args) {
    ExecutorService executor = new ThreadPoolExecutor(3, 3, 0L,
            TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS, new LinkedBlockingQueue<Runnable>(),
            new ThreadPoolExecutor.CallerRunsPolicy());

    log.info("主线程开始执行" + DateUtil.formatDateByPattern(DateUtil.getUnixTime()));
    CompletableFuture<String> future1 =
            CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(() -> {
                try {
                    Thread.sleep(6 * 1000);
                } catch (InterruptedException e) {
                    e.printStackTrace();
                }
                log.info("异步线程1执行完成");
                return "future1";
            }, executor);

    CompletableFuture<String> future2 =
            CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(() -> {
                try {
                    Thread.sleep(10 * 1000);
                } catch (InterruptedException e) {
                    e.printStackTrace();
                }
                log.info("异步线程2执行完成");
                return "future2";
            }, executor);

    CompletableFuture<String> future3 =
            CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(() -> {
                try {
                    Thread.sleep(3 * 1000);
                } catch (InterruptedException e) {
                    e.printStackTrace();
                }
                log.info("异步线程3执行完成");
                return "future3";
            }, executor);
    CompletableFuture.allOf(future1, future2, future3).thenAcceptAsync((Void) -> {
        try {
            log.info("所有异步线程执行完成后触发时间:{}" , DateUtil.formatDateByPattern(DateUtil.getUnixTime()));
            log.info("所有异步线程执行完成后执行结果:{} {} {}" , future1.get(),  future2.get(), future3.get());
