## 概述
* Java的对象拷贝分为两种方式，浅拷贝与深拷贝的区别是深拷贝后的对象是完全独立的对象，源对象内容变化的话是不影响目标对象的
    * 浅拷贝
    * 深拷贝

### 浅拷贝

* 浅拷贝只复制指向某个对象的指针，而不复制对象本身，新旧对象还是共享同一块内存



* 比如`Object` 类的 `clone`方法就是浅拷贝
    *  clone方法首先会判对象是否实现了Cloneable接口，若无则抛出CloneNotSupportedException
* 先来实体类

```java
public class User implements Cloneable {

    private String name;

    private int age;

    private Job job;

    public String getName() {
        return name;
    }

    public void setName(String name) {
        this.name = name;
    }

    public int getAge() {
        return age;
    }

    public void setAge(int age) {
        this.age = age;
    }

    public Job getJob() {
        return job;
    }

    public void setJob(Job job) {
        this.job = job;
    }

    @Override
    public User clone() throws CloneNotSupportedException {
        return (User)super.clone();
    }

    @Override
    public String toString() {
        return "User{" +
                "name='" + name + '\'' +
                ", age=" + age +
                ", job=" + job +
                '}';
    }
}

public class Job {

    private String jobName;

    public Job(String jobName) {
        this.jobName = jobName;
    }

    public String getJobName() {
        return jobName;
    }

    public void setJobName(String jobName) {
        this.jobName = jobName;
    }

    @Override
    public String toString() {
        return "Job{" +
                "jobName='" + jobName + '\'' +
                '}';
    }
}
```

* 测试方法

```java
@Test
public void test1() throws Exception {
    User user1 = new User();
    user1.setName("songsy");
    user1.setAge(100);
    user1.setJob(new Job("猿猴"));

    User user2 = user1.clone();

    System.out.println(user1 == user2);
    System.out.println(user1);
    System.out.println(user2);
    /**
     * user2 是浅拷贝，可以发现job对象只是clone的引用
     */
    user1.setName("songsy改名后");
    user1.getJob().setJobName("猿猴改名后");
    System.out.println(user1);
    System.out.println(user2);
}
```

* 输出结果可以看到是user2 的job对象指向的内容还是和user1 的job对象一样

